did.head: DESCRIPTIVE SUMMARY
did.repository: Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library

scopecontent.head: COLLECTION DESCRIPTION
scopecontent.p: Collection includes reports; letter; station log (1948-1951); minutes of the Cornell Radio Guild, Inc. (1971); Board minutes (1968); published Program Guides (1959-1965); and other materials pertaining to Cornell radio station WVBR and its shows, including Bound For Glory with Phil Shapiro.

prefercite.head: Cite As:
prefercite.p: WVBR records, #35-9-1739. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.
